{"title":"万岁，越南！（二首）","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":8,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁，越南！（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剑歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英勇的越南人民军，杀了美国八只铁鸟，使我想起还剑湖，多少长剑多少浪涛……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是我怀古，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱还剑湖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青青翠竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色儿女；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北方一把剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方一把斧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剑在石上磨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀在火中铸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥刀相寄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血无数，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔到红河岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔到还剑湖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三铮铮革命人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镗镗革命鼓；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红河长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽臂狂舞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长剑能飞天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戳穿纸老虎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁，越南！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红河水你是一面镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照见了我的爱和恨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红河水你是照妖镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照见那豺狼约翰逊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说啥东南亚和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这条狼天天想吃人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是条狼他还带假面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是条狼还想抹脂粉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打死豺狼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才有和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打死豺狼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才有和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红河水你是战士心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是水是热血沸腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打杀八只铁鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界一片欢欣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火里见到了真金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风暴里看到了雄鹰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红河水你是一面镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照出了我的爱和恨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁越南！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁革命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁越南！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁革命！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}